data.description: Welcome to your new home with private access to Lake Houston! This move-in ready home sits on  the 11th hole of Stonebridge golf course in the popular Newport community. Plenty of beautiful mature landscaping, tucked away in a small cul-de-sac. This home offers so much from the front door with tiled entry, split floor plan.  Formal dining room has custom treatments and is very accommodating in size. The community of Newport offers 18 hole golf course, swimming pool, tennis courts, clubhouse, bar/grill, workout area, horse stables, parks and trails, private lake and river access. Close commute to downtown, medical, shopping. Don't miss out and stop by today!
